            </div>
            <div class="edu">
              <span class="year"> &nbsp;2023&nbsp; </span><br />
              <div class="grad">INTERMEDIATE-(92.4%)</div>
              <p class="aboutgrad">
                I Have Completed My Intermediate From L.N. Public School, Hapur
